snippet: Three friends of an alleged victim of a gang rape at a University of Virginia frat house told The Associated Press that a magazine article about the events of the night in question was wrong on a number of key points....

headline.print_headline: Key Points U.Va. Students Say Rape Story Got Wrong
headline.main: Key Points U.Va. Students Say Rape Story Got Wrong

lead_paragraph: Three friends of an alleged victim of a gang rape at a University of Virginia frat house told The Associated Press that a magazine article about the events of the night in question was wrong on a number of key points.
